des: Your host today is Leon Birdstein, band leader of the newly formed All-Star Animal Orchestra. He’s assembled the four best music groups in the animal kingdom: The Wolf Gang, The Technocats, Moo'd Muzic! and finally, the wild card of the bunch...The Chimpan-zanies! Together with your help, they will create fun songs, mashing up instruments from different musical genres – over 700 possible musical combinations to explore!
